<section id="primary_content">
	
	<h1>The Crew</h1>
	
	<div class="abstract">
		<p>We love the Interweb, but to solve challenges people also need to get together. Hooking up with likeminded folk at a gig or social, or just for a cuppa and a natter is the Good for Nothing way.</p>
		<p>We're hatching local chapters to help good folk do just that. If we're not near you yet and you'd like to bring Good for Nothing to your hood, <a href="mailto:hello@goodfornothing.com">drop us a note</a>, we'd love to talk.</p>
	</div>
	
	<ul class="grid_list">
		<% @all_chapters.each do |chapter| %>
			<li>
				<h3><%= chapter.title %></h3>
				<p><%= chapter.users.crew.map{ |u| link_to u['name'], member_path(u) }.join(', ').html_safe %></p>
			</li>	
		<% end %>
	</ul>
	
</section>

<aside id="secondary_content">
	<p class="cta"><%= link_to "Chapter calendar", calendar_path %></p>
</aside>